description:
qualifier that specifies a method of selecting or computing a representative value from more than one value.
1 The qualifier can be used to express a defined type of average in conjunction with a defined data element type or a defined data value 
2 The qualifier can be used in all those cases if the type of the average used in the existing definitions of data element types is not sufficiently specified 
3 The value codes can be used as subscript to the preferred symbol of the related quantitative data element type
4 The value list is an open list. Other values not listed need to be agreed among the partners.
